## File location rules
Create all files in the folder most relevant to the heading they are in. Use subfolders for any nested routes


## Page rules
### No H1 title
Don't use an H1 title anywhere. The file will automatically render a title from the frontmatter

### Frontmatter
Create all .mdx files with frontmatter like the below. The title should quickly describe what the page discusses. The description should give a quick, clear, insightful description

---
title: "Get Started"
description: "Use Zeus to build high quality AI agents"
---

